featured_reviews.review_id: It is a very big mosque in Memari.It is two storied .Very beautiful this is.This is the mosque of Jamia Islamia Madinatul Uloom madrasha.It is based on hanafi mazhab.Golam Ahmed Mortaza is the secretary of this.Air condition is available in some part of this mosque.A beautiful garden also located beside this .There is a place to do uzu. There is a tall minaret that can be seen from afar. During winter, the whole mosque is covered with carpet .Jamia and Mamoon's students come here for prayers and some people from outside come to pray.
